      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "Male human Sable Company Captain",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> the last commandant of the Sable Company — the man who put an arrow in the queen's eye before all Korvosa and watched her smile. Found in the secret cell E14 (@Check[type:perception|dc:41] for the door, +15 with the E20 records; Kordaitra's key or @Check[type:thievery|dc:30] — a good lock): unconscious, kept at death's edge by Kordaitra's visits, and <strong>feebleminded</strong>. Healed, he cringes like a beaten animal until the curse is lifted; cured and re-armed, @Check[type:diplomacy|dc:30] enlists him (@Check[type:intimidation|dc:30] works, but he bolts at first chance). <strong>Rescue = a full encounter's XP</strong>; his survival galvanizes the rebellion.</p>",
      "privateNotes": ""
